# Mastodon

A [todo.txt][1] parser.

[1]: http://ginatrapani.github.com/todo.txt-cli/

## Installation

    sudo gem install mastodon

## Usage

    require 'mastodon'
    mast = Mastodon.new(File.readlines("todo.txt"))
    # List all the projects
    mast.projects
    # List all the contexts
    mast.contexts

